data.description: Home is in a quiet neighborhood closed to everything,  house recently had the driveway and front entrance cleaned, sealed and painted, we are in the process to paint the house in the inside and outside to give it a fresh look, we recently cleaned and sealed the pavers in the pool area and the fire pit area as well. Pretty soon we will post more pics when we get it done!!!
